on clay court though he was believed to be stronger on faster
courts. He also finished semi-finalist at this year's London and
Copenhagen open tourneys.
</P>
<P>
The winner of the Dutch-Belgian tie will next meet in the world
group quarter-finals the winner of the United States-Russia tie.
</P>
<P>
