</P>
<P>
Guangzhou: min. 23 degrees C., max. 30 degrees C., cloudy, calm
to gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
Hong Kong: min. 20 degrees C., max. 28 degrees C., cloudy, calm
to gentle breeze.  
</P>
