village, inhabited by tribe people, who tend cattle and sheep, and
several other choppers had to turn back because of the strong
winds.
</P>
<P>
Official sources in the province said the residents might have
been completely engulfed by the mud and were unlikely to survive
should rescue not arrive on time.
</P>
<P>
Heavy rains during the past week have cause floods in the area,
cut off roads and destroyed bridges. 
