injured, which include at least a dozen protesters and 22
policemen. Fifteen protesters were detained for interrogation.
</P>
<P>
This was one of the worst Arab rioting in the past years
between Israeli police and Arab citizens, who have been
protesting discrimination and confiscation of properties by
Israeli authorities.
</P>
<P>
The 1 million Israeli Arabs closely associate themselves with
the Palestinians in the territories and support their struggle
against Israeli occupation.
</P>
<P>
Last Monday, Arabs across Israel observed a general strike and
held protests to mark the Land Day, dedicated to six Arabs killed
in the 1976 suppression of an Arab rioting against Israel's
confiscation of land. 
