<HEADLINE> China's Chemical Fiber Production Increases </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, April 5 (Xinhua) -- The latest figures from the State
Statistics Bureau show that China produced 346,100 tons of
chemical fiber in January, up 7.2 percent over the same period of
1997.
</P>
<P>
The output of synthetic fiber hit 311,000 tons, up 8.1
